= About iBlah =

iBlah is a free software to send instance message to desktop computer or cellphone for Mac OS.
China Mobile Fetion Protocol compatible with iBlah.

iBlah publish with BSD license.

iBlah - 免费发即时信息到手机或电脑 Mac OS 客户端；中国移动飞信协议兼容 iBlah 。

iBlah 使用 BSD 许可发布。

== FEATURES ==

- login with {cellphone No., fetion No.}
- auto choose last login account and fill passwd in encryption
- switch status to {{available, away, busy}, invisible, offline}
- send message to client, receive from {client, cellphone}
- add friend by {cellphone No., fetion No.}


== Up & Usage ==

For MacOS 10.6

install MacPort

port install py27-pyqt4

/opt/local/bin/python2.7 iblah.py



== RUNTIME REQUIREMENT ==

>= Python-2.6
>= PyQt-4.6

== BUILD REQUIREMENT ==

>= Python-2.6
>= PyQt-4.6
>= QtDesigner-4.7


== convert Qt UI file to python script ==

python scripts/create_ui.py

== convert image file to python script  ==

(QRC, Qt Resource Compiler)

python script/compile_qrc.py

== convert Balsamiq Mockups file to png ==

http://balsamiq.com/


== 快捷键 ==

| esc | 关闭标签页（聊天窗口内），关闭窗口（如果是最后一个标签页） |
| enter | 登录；换行（聊天窗口内） |
| ⌘-enter | 发送信息 |
| ⌘-= | 添加好友 |
| ⌘-i | 显示联系人信息 |
| ⌘-[1-9] | 切换到标签页[1-9]（聊天窗口内） |
| ⌘-] | 切换到下一个标签页（聊天窗口内） |
| ⌘-[ | 切换到上一个标签页（聊天窗口内） |

从系统继承

| ⌘-q | 关闭程序 |
| ⌘-h | 隐藏程序窗口 |
